{"tid":2236813,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟有抑鬱係咪死路一條","createTime":"2020-10-09T18:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T06:28:33.000Z","uid":302347,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf5481cbde03ccf195a8660935782518042eef7","tid":2236813,"uid":302347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:07:35.000Z","msg":"成世都係其他人嘅負累，淨係會麻煩到人、令人唔開心、講嘢傷害到人，真係好撚仆街。<br />\n真係好希望呢個世界從來都冇我呢個人，我完全係多鳩餘。但係又驚自殺會麻煩到身邊嘅人，其實可以點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b52f5c2c08416b3f5065c5bcb6122c95372ad2a","tid":2236813,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:11:33.000Z","msg":"仲可以痛苦既生存落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ea03fe7049976fce3269f51de3112155ff8f76","tid":2236813,"uid":302347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b52f5c2c08416b3f5065c5bcb6122c95372ad2a","tid":2236813,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:11:33.000Z","msg":"仲可以痛苦既生存落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"真係同你個名一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2453ca741004dec4a2609cfcf0c22a2cbd6ebf92","tid":2236813,"uid":139173,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"咩料啊<br />\n覺得自己做得唔好咪將目標分幾段囉<br />\n想考100分咪分5段囉<br />\n叫春有用嘅話人人唔使努力啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c67d55789f7bb3c5c0472a23a311e1c0421761","tid":2236813,"uid":318359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T18:14:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec